.TH VITTE-EDITOR 1 "March 2026" "vitte 03.2025" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
vitte-editor \- graphical multi-file editor for Vitte projects
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B vitte-editor
[\fIproject-or-file\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B vitte-editor
launches the VitteEditor desktop application.
It provides multi-file tabs, syntax highlighting, completion suggestions,
and diagnostics via
.B vitte check --diag-json
.
.SH EXIT STATUS
Returns 0 on successful launch, non-zero if startup fails.
.SH ENVIRONMENT
Inherits the same runtime/toolchain environment as
.BR vitte (1)
(notably \fBVITTE_ROOT\fR when diagnostics or project checks are invoked).
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
vitte-editor
vitte-editor /path/to/project
vitte-editor src/main.vit
.fi
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR vitte (1),
.BR vittec (1),
.BR vitte-linker (1)
